OL,3,CChinese 'mega-embassy' approved by
OL,4,Cgovernment on former Royal Mint site
OL,6,FThe government has given China the
OL,7,Fgreen light to build a new "mega
OL,8,Fembassy" at the former Royal Mint site
OL,9,Fin central London.
OL,11,FBejing's plans have been subject to
OL,12,Fcontroversy - with campaigners raising
OL,13,Fconcerns for local residents' safety
OL,14,Fand issues of national security.
OL,16,FLocal Government Secretary Steve Reed
OL,17,Fapproved the plans for the building at
OL,18,FRoyal Mint Court, near the Tower of
OL,19,FLondon on Tuesday morning.
