OL,3,CChinese 'mega-embassy' approved by
OL,4,Cgovernment on former Royal Mint site
OL,6,FThe decision removes a diplomatic
OL,7,Fhurdle in the relationship with Xi
OL,8,FJinping's government, clearing the way
OL,9,Ffor Sir Keir Starmer to make a widely-
OL,10,Fexpected visit to China ` possibly
OL,11,Fwithin weeks.
OL,13,FPlans include 208 secret rooms and a
OL,14,Fhidden chamber, according to reporting
OL,15,Fby The Telegraph.
OL,17,FCritics fear the secret rooms, located
OL,18,Fin the site's basement, could be used
OL,19,Ffor the detention of dissidents who
OL,20,Fhave fled the Chinese state for
OL,21,FBritain.
