OL,6,FThe hidden chamber would meanwhile be
OL,7,Flocated in close proximity to data
OL,8,Fcables said to be crucial for
OL,9,Ffinancial sector communications
OL,10,Fbetween the City of London and Canary
OL,11,FWharf.
OL,13,FWhat makes it a "mega embassy"?
OL,15,FThe new embassy would cover 22,000
OL,16,Fsquare meters on the site of the
OL,17,Fformer Royal Mint and would make it
OL,18,Fthe largest in Europe.
OL,20,FCurrently, China has several sites
OL,21,Faround the capital:
