OL,6,FThe new embassy plans put all of these
OL,7,Fbuildings under one roof.
OL,9,FBut last week, Ciaran Martin, former
OL,10,Fchief executive of GCHQ's National
OL,11,FCyber Security Centre, dismissed
OL,12,Fconcerns about the proposed embassy's
OL,13,Flocation.
OL,15,FIn an article for The Times, he said
OL,16,Fthe plans would have been thoroughly
OL,17,Fscrutinised by the UK's security
OL,18,Fservices, and that "no Government
OL,19,Fwould override their advice were they
OL,20,Fto say the risks were too great".
