OL,6,FThe government has argued that they
OL,7,Fnew embassy would mean China's
OL,8,Fdiplomatic presence would condense
OL,9,Ffrom seven buildings to one, which
OL,10,Fcould have security benefits.
OL,12,FHowever, MPs including from within
OL,13,FLabour ranks have warned that the
OL,14,Fembassy could also be used to "step up
OL,15,Fintimidation" against dissidents and
OL,16,Fhave urged Communities Secretary Steve
OL,17,FReed to block the application.
