OL,6,FAddressing the Commons on the eve of
OL,7,Fthe decision deadline, Foreign Office
OL,8,Fminister Seema Malhotra said: "We've
OL,9,Fbeen consistently clear that national
OL,10,Fsecurity is the first duty of
OL,11,Fgovernment, and it has been our core
OL,12,Fpriority throughout the embassy
OL,13,Fprocess, with the close involvement of
OL,14,Fthe security and intelligence
OL,15,Fagencies."
