OL,6,FShe said a "range of measures" had
OL,7,Fbeen implemented to protect national
OL,8,Fsecurity and that she had "full
OL,9,Fconfidence" in the security services
OL,10,Fto be able to manage potential risks
OL,11,Ffrom spies.
OL,13,FDespite the government's decision,
OL,14,Fcampaigners have vowed to continue
OL,15,Fprotesting.
OL,17,FTreasurer of Royal Mint Court
OL,18,FResident's Association, Mark Nygate,
OL,19,Fsaid: "The residents are determined to
OL,20,Fkeep fighting today's decision.
