OL,6,F"Along with our diaspora partners we
OL,7,Fhave reached out worldwide with our
OL,8,Fstory, and highlighted the issues and
OL,9,Fearlier legal opinions that will be
OL,10,Fthe basis for our challenge."
OL,12,FThe Inter-Parliamentary Alliance on
OL,13,FChina, which has been involved in a
OL,14,Fcampaign to halt the new Chinese
OL,15,Fembassy, said the planning approval
OL,16,Fwas the "wrong decision for the UK".
