OL,6,FLuke de Pulford, a co-founder of the
OL,7,Fgroup, said: "This is the wrong
OL,8,Fdecision for the UK, sending all the
OL,9,Fwrong signals. Wrong for dissidents,
OL,10,Fwrong for UK national security.
OL,12,F"Our three Cs China policy is less
OL,13,Fcompete, challenge and cooperate, more
OL,14,Fcover-up, cave in, and cash out."
